Moraine Lake Logjam



If you're going to come to Moraine Lake, take one photo, and leave, it would be from here. It was difficult to find a time when so few people were visible.
Taken Wednesday, August 19, 2009, 09:10:52AM. Original image size: 2592x3888, 2.0Mb
Technical details: Canon EOS 40D, 1/125s@ F11, ISO 100, 15mm f/2.8 Fisheye (24mm equiv)
PS CS2 Exp0.5, RC-30
